# 🎓 Thrincs Demo
### Certificados Digitales Verificables en Blockchain

<p align="center">

![Blockchain](https://img.shields.io/badge/Blockchain-Ethereum-blue)
![Framework](https://img.shields.io/badge/Framework-Hardhat-orange)
![Standard](https://img.shields.io/badge/Standard-ERC721-purple)
![Token](https://img.shields.io/badge/Token-Soulbound-red)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Demo-green)

